      <title>火山烟雾导致菲律宾首都学校停课</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/volcanic-smog-forces-school-suspensions-in-philippine-capital</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾首都南部的一座活火山产生的烟雾导致学校停课，部分地区的空气质量达到“非常不健康”的水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/volcanic-smog-forces-school-suspensions-in-philippine-capital</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 09:32:03 GMT</pubDate>
